<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/criminal-injuries-compensation-authority> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "CICA pays compensation to people physically or mentally injured because of a violent crime in England, Scotland or Wales, or in an act of terror abroad. CICA is an executive agency, sponsored by the Ministry of Justice ."@en .
